      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "11.1 可再生能源和不可再生能源",
        "text_hash": "7d3b618607872fcaee2ffbf94b6e09a2290356a380840a556787f18c9ef0c43f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c78cb344c87a9de67c9bb198",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "物质与材料词汇表",
        "text_hash": "e796f131a2bd54b9bcd21dd447c6079d57630cef11a5740da39c2697808c655c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_36690085226c3bc4e0176fa3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "abundant：当某物大量存在或可获得时；丰富的",
        "text_hash": "11443e27d4e3e98607505d6af08bc9a6ff968f0ce7a05f0e1b29e78daaca63c2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ebd3c22714e353121222b4b9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "acid：一种具有腐蚀性、有酸味，并且在手指间感觉粗糙（有抓附感）的物质",
        "text_hash": "723ff644b002f1b07e421a258151109e98f6d307e0092199aa97e610dc8e9216",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_90ad1f752f9a8ed2b72547cb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "alkali：溶解在水中的碱",
        "text_hash": "cf3433ede9240cbcbe95886c3d0877760e982aa2a2c294d12ab97ef0acb1ec83",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9cdc44553fac17012f7c9a57",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "alloy：两种或更多金属的混合物（不锈钢是合金的一个例子）",
        "text_hash": "15a5c5a7777759ab2c7b9780d318418e684b337a1f3520408041bb9bc965597c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fbc28166454024c461ce5479",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "altitude：一个地方高出海平面的高度；内陆地区或山上的地方被认为比海岸上的地方海拔更高",
        "text_hash": "bb8094375f359f7ae48cf5af2d704e652ca94a05db30e95d7a59318ae4a448ec",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cacbdcfa4c2d577f4cfce0e6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "ascorbic acid：存在于某些水果和蔬菜中的天然酸；也称为维生素 C",
        "text_hash": "c5690c546c87e0f6c1d57bcbdf224473497db780a9d1e7847c7d5752416970e1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_994c8635a9fcd369df100c72",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "atomic number：表示某一给定元素并显示其在元素周期表中位置的唯一数字",
        "text_hash": "92c9ad6ab540060d5599a259cca17de449c623188f2d0e12699cc502b14ddea2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_81ea9ae089934d3d7a62db3c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "base：一种也可能具有腐蚀性、有苦味，并且在手指间感觉滑腻的物质",
        "text_hash": "99a901a16ae6fbf24414b11b574a854aeaf0f98969a9cd5263ea382606307ab3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3c438452c8f2d71d2110b90b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "boiling point：某种特定材料从液态变为气态（沸腾）时的温度",
        "text_hash": "9ac4ac36e2aa3e947f7c827495be7b215ded3fd9e9fa255ced0fcad176a4158d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f2024583fce36826170cc067",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "capillary action：液体在细管中被向上吸引的过程",
        "text_hash": "4ad868d8a270a0846a85732fef039498fad1395c3fa74633a83404f8d4f91ab6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0faa0a780137e3f940f885ac",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "chemical formula：使用符号表示化学物质的方式，这些符号告诉我们一种化合物含有哪些元素以及它们的比例",
        "text_hash": "3999bcf576af4c4117d1ebfd5fa6fc9c623cd2dafce0aba4017b6421ed833365",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5e818d8f2db67078a237141b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "chemoreceptor：检测化学信号的感觉神经细胞或感觉器官",
        "text_hash": "032f3d9ac6b0c21a1b0ea16e04434bd71b14c6711f5fee7c3ba61d4ffce40c56",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_da9539012b5b907bdb271c5e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "chromatogram：由通过色谱法分离出来的成分在纸上形成的图案",
        "text_hash": "50a478718f9677e97bf5f37104bd6c345927ef335afb685be3fe8a56386779b5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4fa2806c90db0dbc61cd8098",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "chromatography：一种由液体携带的混合物被分离成各组成部分的过程",
        "text_hash": "dcb20c881086a3a2a5803cd925fcea71c8e3a20f2f868f02c8d6217111b1c557",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_678bded3fcb467b96c87f54e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "citric acid：存在于柑橘类水果中的天然酸",
        "text_hash": "d0f70673dbf43e40df58a48196bd0fee96b4207e749c9f196943ea721faaea92",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_229f5ab3611aad1459debb4c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "clear：透明的；可看透的",
        "text_hash": "6dce9e9258d8d7f28609f9d3c7f4f86282594840aa4d40ff6baa3dc6fd5ce5e1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e924390a733f3aadc42b4d33"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    }
  ],
